# RogueCFA.ai — Environment Variables
# ====================================
# Most API keys (Finnhub, LLM BYOK keys) are provided by users through the browser UI
# and stored exclusively in their browser's localStorage.
#
# For server-side database storage (Task 3.5: BNN MarketCall Picks & Analyst Track Record),
# configure the following Supabase variables in your .env.local file and Vercel dashboard:

SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsIn...your-service-role-secret-key

